 exclusion results for the scalar\nsector of the Randall-Sundrum model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Dec 2010 10:34:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Jan 2011 09:58:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
